-- Tata Motors Increases Share Sale's Size by 43% to $750 Million to Cut Debt
-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 2010-10-04T04:51:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/tata-motors-increases-share-sale-s-size-by-43-to-750-million-to-cut-debt.html
Tata Motors Ltd. increased the size
of a share sale to large investors to $750 million from $525
million, according to a statement on the Bombay Stock Exchange
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
